## Task: V2: Database schema — tasks, attempts, attempt_logs tables

Add new SQLite tables: tasks (id, title, source, project_dir, created_at), attempts (id, task_id, started_at, ended_at, result, project_dir), attempt_logs (attempt_id, workflow, step_name, file_path, file_type, file_size). Refactor the runs table to track step executions with an attempt_id column. Update RunStore interface and SQLite adapter.
